column5: Since my computer crashed I lost everything. My address book is almost empty. So please if you want me to be able to contact you by email, send me one. [email protected] so I can add you to my address book.
cheap viagra or nigerian scam....?  G

guess I'll be banned by sunrise...
And I'm on Mod Q...I'm surprised this post got through.
No worries, i"ll take care of it

I got these pill from some nice fellas overseas and now the wife won't leave me alone.. she's driving me crazy.  Good news though, I am now named properly for the right reasons!  Good fishing,  BIG Cliff"

have you tried a re-send yet? Mine went through OK.  But I picked the address from my contacts list, not a copy/paste from here. I used [email protected]  and that seems to be the same as Cliff posted above.
